{"tid":2384603,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"便衣警潛入大學搜證　被學生識破「反監禁」3小時　副校加入審問","createTime":"2021-01-28T15:41:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T18:01:06.000Z","uid":261647,"like":77,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"91ca6b1851b743ddcd9d4507a04de73af5db7672","tid":2384603,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T15:41:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20141106/422446.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20141106%2F422446.htm&d=YX1qj72dVL8lCt3J0nVEUr3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=862f46d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20141106/422446.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cbg9h7U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCbg9h7U.png&h=e11fe5da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據《ANN NEWS》報導，由於日前有日本民眾在東京銀座舉辦「反戰、反安倍」的抗議活動，當時警視廳逮捕的學生中有兩名京都大學的學生，因此，才會在4日派便衣警察進入京大吉田校區蒐證，沒想到最後反被學生監禁。<br />\n<br />\n京都大學學生發現員警的「真實身分」後，就把對方帶到教室關起來，甚至派出多名學生輪流「訊問」，最後就連京大的副校長也加入審問。京都府警方獲報後，派出數十名機動員警前往「案發現場」，現場氣氛一度降到冰點，而這名「被綁」的員警也在被監禁3小時後獲釋，整起事件無人傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n京都大學事後發表聲明，表示警方偷偷潛入校園的舉動已嚴重侵害大學自治，校方感到十分遺憾。由於日本大學的學生運動風氣盛行，這次警方引起許多網友關注，還有人直接在推特「圖文齊發」做實況轉播。"},{"pid":"add03b74f99fa0592f5ba927b030d817bb46db21","tid":2384603,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T15:45:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0d227a0988c0cd0f3f5c4e5baece8c49be3844d","tid":2384603,"uid":126642,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T15:45:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 喺香港可能已經出動SDU救人"},{"pid":"071862ed98f8d882f2c3027ba16fe85b0f1f5d15","tid":2384603,"uid":36906,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T15:46:04.000Z","msg":"反安倍?????????"},{"pid":"d85fbb986b38585a4a48b2ab15e2b5e8c3a5bbdb","tid":2384603,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy"